<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Vibe Check — Product Case Study by Sanyukta Jha</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,wght@0,300;0,600;0,900;1,300;1,600&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{
  --gold:#C8A96E;--gold2:rgba(200,169,110,0.15);--gold3:rgba(200,169,110,0.08);
  --dark:#0C0C0C;--dark2:#121212;--dark3:#1A1A1A;--dark4:#222;
  --text:#F5F0E8;--text2:rgba(245,240,232,0.65);--text3:rgba(245,240,232,0.35);--text4:rgba(245,240,232,0.15);
  --red:#E24B4A;--green:#639922;--blue:#378ADD;--purple:#8B5CF6;
  --border:rgba(245,240,232,0.08);--border2:rgba(245,240,232,0.14);
}
html,body{width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;background:var(--dark);font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif;color:var(--text)}
.deck{width:100vw;height:100vh;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.slide{position:absolute;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;padding:52px 80px 80px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity 0.55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1),transform 0.55s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1);transform:translateY(24px)}
.slide.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:all;transform:translateY(0)}
.slide.exit-up{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-24px);pointer-events:none}
.slide-inner{width:100%;max-width:1140px;height:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}

/* PROGRESS & NAV */
.progress{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),#E8C98E);transition:width 0.4s ease;z-index:300}
.nav{position:fixed;bottom:28px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;z-index:200;background:rgba(18,18,18,0.92);backdrop-filter:blur(24px);border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:100px;padding:10px 20px}
.nav-btn{background:none;border:none;color:var(--text3);font-size:16px;cursor:pointer;padding:3px 8px;transition:color 0.2s;line-height:1;font-family:'DM Sans',sans-serif}
.nav-btn:hover{color:var(--gold)}
.counter{font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);min-width:48px;text-align:center;letter-spacing:0.05em}
.dots{display:flex;gap:5px}
.dot{width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--text4);cursor:pointer;transition:all 0.25s}
.dot.active{background:var(--gold);width:18px;border-radius:3px}
.key-hint{position:fixed;top:20px;right:24px;font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);display:flex;gap:6px}
.key{background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:5px;padding:2px 7px;font-size:10px}
.slide-tag{position:absolute;top:28px;left:80px;font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);opacity:0.8}

/* TYPOGRAPHY */
.eyebrow{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:14px}
.display{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;line-height:1.05;color:var(--text)}
.serif{font-family:'Fraunces',serif}
.body{font-size:16px;line-height:1.72;color:var(--text2);font-weight:300}
.small{font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text3)}
.source{font-size:10px;color:var(--text3);letter-spacing:0.04em;margin-top:4px}

/* LAYOUT */
.two-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;width:100%;align-items:start}
.three-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:24px;width:100%}
.four-col{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:20px;width:100%}
.l-heavy{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.5fr 1fr;gap:56px;width:100%;align-items:center}
.r-heavy{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1.5fr;gap:56px;width:100%;align-items:center}
.split-60{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.6fr 1fr;gap:48px;width:100%;align-items:start}

/* CARDS */
.card{background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:24px 28px}
.card-gold{background:var(--gold3);border:0.5px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.25);border-radius:18px;padding:24px 28px}
.card-sm{background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px}
.pill{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px;border:0.5px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.3);color:var(--gold)}
.pill-gray{display:inline-block;font-size:11px;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px;border:0.5px solid var(--border2);color:var(--text3)}
.tag-row{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin-top:10px}

/* STAT */
.stat-big{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:56px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gold);line-height:1}
.stat-med{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:40px;font-weight:700;color:var(--gold);line-height:1}
.stat-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.4}

/* QUOTE */
.q-block{border-left:3px solid var(--gold);padding:4px 0 4px 24px;margin:8px 0}
.q-text{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5}
.q-attr{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:8px}

/* TABLE */
.comp-tbl{width:100%;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0;font-size:13px}
.comp-tbl th{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text3);padding:10px 14px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border2)}
.comp-tbl th:first-child{text-align:left}
.comp-tbl td{padding:10px 14px;text-align:center;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.comp-tbl td:first-child{text-align:left;color:var(--text2);font-size:13px}
.vc-col{background:var(--gold3);border-left:1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2);border-right:1px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.2)}
.chk{color:var(--gold);font-weight:600;font-size:15px}
.crs{color:var(--text4);font-size:15px}
.prt{font-size:11px;color:var(--blue)}

/* LAYER CARD */
.layer{background:var(--dark2);border-radius:14px;padding:20px 24px;border-left:3px solid var(--gold);margin-bottom:12px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start}
.layer-num{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:900;color:var(--gold);line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;width:36px}
.layer-body{}
.layer-title{font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:5px}
.layer-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.6}
.layer-tag{display:inline-block;font-size:10px;padding:2px 8px;border-radius:100px;background:var(--gold2);color:var(--gold);margin-top:8px;margin-right:4px}

/* PERSONA */
.persona{background:var(--dark3);border-radius:18px;padding:22px 26px;border:0.5px solid var(--border);position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.persona::after{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),transparent)}
.persona-name{font-size:17px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:2px}
.persona-role{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:12px}
.persona-quote{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:14px;font-style:italic;color:var(--text2);margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.5}
.persona-need{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5}

/* ITERATION */
.iter-item{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;padding:14px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.iter-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.iter-badge{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:3px 10px;border-radius:100px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px}
.v-done{background:rgba(99,153,34,0.12);color:var(--green);border:0.5px solid rgba(99,153,34,0.25)}
.v-fix{background:rgba(226,75,74,0.1);color:var(--red);border:0.5px solid rgba(226,75,74,0.2)}
.v-gold{background:var(--gold2);color:var(--gold);border:0.5px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.3)}

/* ARROW FLOW */
.flow{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.flow-step{background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:100px;padding:8px 16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text);white-space:nowrap}
.flow-arr{color:var(--gold);font-size:18px;flex-shrink:0}
.flow-step.highlight{background:var(--gold2);border-color:rgba(200,169,110,0.4);color:var(--gold)}

/* PHONE FRAME */
.phone{width:320px;flex-shrink:0;background:var(--dark2);border-radius:32px;padding:8px;border:1.5px solid var(--border2);box-shadow:0 32px 64px rgba(0,0,0,0.6)}
.phone-inner{border-radius:26px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:9/19;background:var(--dark)}
.phone-inner img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}

/* BG GLOWS */
.glow{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(90px);pointer-events:none;z-index:0}
.glow-g{background:rgba(200,169,110,0.09)}
.glow-r{background:rgba(226,75,74,0.06)}
.glow-b{background:rgba(55,138,221,0.07)}

/* REWARD BARS */
.reward-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.reward-row:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.rr-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);flex:1}
.rr-bar-bg{flex:2;height:5px;background:var(--dark4);border-radius:3px;overflow:hidden}
.rr-bar-fill{height:100%;border-radius:3px}
.rr-pts{font-size:12px;color:var(--gold);font-weight:500;width:60px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}
.rr-coins{font-size:12px;color:var(--blue);width:54px;text-align:right;flex-shrink:0}

/* METRIC CARD */
.metric{background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:16px 20px}
.metric-name{font-size:14px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px}
.metric-desc{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.5}
.metric-type{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:6px}

/* ANIMATIONS */
@keyframes up{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes fade{from{opacity:0}to{opacity:1}}
@keyframes scale{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(0.96)}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}}
.slide.active .a{animation:up 0.45s cubic-bezier(.4,0,.2,1) both}
.slide.active .a1{animation-delay:.08s}
.slide.active .a2{animation-delay:.16s}
.slide.active .a3{animation-delay:.24s}
.slide.active .a4{animation-delay:.32s}
.slide.active .a5{animation-delay:.40s}
.slide.active .a6{animation-delay:.48s}
.slide.active .a7{animation-delay:.56s}
.slide.active .af{animation:fade 0.4s ease both}
.slide.active .as{animation:scale 0.4s ease both}

/* DIVIDER LINE */
.hr{height:0.5px;background:var(--border2);margin:16px 0}
.hr-gold{height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--gold),transparent);margin:20px 0}

/* PROBLEM BOX */
.problem-box{background:var(--dark2);border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 32px}

/* CHECK / CROSS LIST */
.check-item{display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;padding:10px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.check-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.ci-icon{flex-shrink:0;width:20px;font-size:14px;margin-top:1px}
.ci-text{font-size:14px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5}
.ci-sub{font-size:12px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px}

/* PHASE2 ITEM */
.p2-item{display:flex;gap:16px;align-items:flex-start;padding:12px 0;border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--border)}
.p2-item:last-child{border-bottom:none}
.p2-icon{font-size:22px;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.p2-title{font-size:15px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:3px}
.p2-desc{font-size:13px;color:var(--text3);line-height:1.5}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="progress" id="prog"></div>
<div class="key-hint"><span class="key">←</span><span class="key">→</span></div>

<div class="deck" id="deck">

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 01: COVER -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide active" id="s0">
  <div class="glow glow-g" style="width:700px;height:700px;top:-150px;right:-150px"></div>
  <div class="glow glow-r" style="width:400px;height:400px;bottom:-100px;left:-100px"></div>
  <div class="slide-inner" style="position:relative;z-index:1;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 0">
    <div>
      <div class="eyebrow a a1">Product Case Study · 2025</div>
      <div class="display a a2" style="font-size:100px;font-weight:900;line-height:0.92;margin-bottom:20px">Vibe<br><span style="color:var(--gold);font-style:italic">Check.</span></div>
      <div class="body a a3" style="font-size:20px;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:32px">A real-time vibe discovery app that tells you what a place actually feels like right now — not what it looked like 2 years ago.</div>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;flex-wrap:wrap" class="a a4">
        <span class="pill">Consumer Product</span>
        <span class="pill">Discovery &amp; Social</span>
        <span class="pill">Real-time · Community-powered</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="a a5" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between">
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text)">Sanyukta Jha</div>
        <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:2px">Business Analyst, Amazon</div>
        <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);margin-top:4px">sanyukta.jha105@gmail.com</div>
        <div style="margin-top:12px;display:flex;gap:10px">
          <a href="https://github.com/sanyukta-jha" target="_blank" style="background:var(--gold2);border:0.5px solid rgba(200,169,110,0.4);border-radius:100px;padding:7px 18px;font-size:12px;color:var(--gold);text-decoration:none">🔗 View Prototype</a>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sanyuktajha/" target="_blank" style="background:var(--dark3);border:0.5px solid var(--border2);border-radius:100px;padding:7px 18px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text2);text-decoration:none">LinkedIn</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align:right">
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-bottom:4px">Prototype built &amp; tested</div>
        <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3)">35 user interviews · 4 iterations · 2 test rounds</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 02: THE NIGHT IT STARTED -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s1">
  <div class="glow glow-g" style="width:600px;height:600px;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
  <div class="slide-tag">Origin</div>
  <div class="slide-inner" style="position:relative;z-index:1">
    <div class="eyebrow a a1">Where this started</div>
    <div class="l-heavy">
      <div>
        <div class="display a a2" style="font-size:48px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:28px;line-height:1.1">One bad night out sparked a product idea.</div>
        <div class="body a a3" style="margin-bottom:20px">It was my one-year work anniversary. I spent time getting ready, checked Google Maps, read the reviews — "great ambience," four stars, beautiful photos. Took an Uber. Walked in.</div>
        <div class="body a a4" style="margin-bottom:20px">The place was completely dead. No music. Nobody there. The food was decent, the decor was nice — but the energy just wasn't there. Nothing online had warned me. Everything still showed four stars and "great ambience."</div>
        <div class="body a a5">I went back to Google Maps that night. Everything still said the same thing. There was nowhere — not one place — that could tell me what a venue felt like <em>on that specific night.</em> That gap is what I built Vibe Check to close.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="a a3" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px">
        <div class="card-gold" style="padding:22px 26px">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;margin-bottom:10px">What Google Maps showed</div>
          <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;margin-bottom:8px">
            <div style="color:#FFB800;font-size:16px">★★★★</div>
            <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--text)">4.2 stars</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);font-style:italic;line-height:1.5">"Great ambience, beautiful interior, perfect for a night out..."</div>
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text3);margin-top:8px">Review from 3 weeks ago</div>
        </div>
        <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:28px;color:var(--gold)">↓</div>
        <div class="card" style="border-color:rgba(226,75,74,0.2);border-left:3px solid var(--red)">
          <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--red);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.12em;margin-bottom:10px">What I walked into</div>
          <div style="font-size:20px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">Completely dead.</div>
          <div style="font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.5">No music. Empty tables. Zero energy. Friday night at 9pm.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 03: THE PROBLEM -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s2">
  <div class="slide-tag">Problem</div>
  <div class="slide-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow a a1">The problem</div>
    <div class="display a a2" style="font-size:52px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:36px;line-height:1.05;max-width:800px">Every discovery tool shows you a place's best day. None show you what it's like right now — at this moment, on this day.</div>
    <div class="three-col">
      <div class="card a a3" style="border-top:3px solid var(--red)">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:14px">⭐</div>
        <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">Ratings are stale</div>
        <div class="body" style="font-size:14px">A 4-star review written 3 weeks ago tells you nothing about whether the place is buzzing or dead <em>tonight.</em> Yet that's the primary signal people use.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card a a4" style="border-top:3px solid var(--gold)">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:14px">📸</div>
        <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">Photos are curated</div>
        <div class="body" style="font-size:14px">Venue photos are professionally shot on their best day. They show full tables and great lighting — not the empty Tuesday when you happen to show up.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card a a5" style="border-top:3px solid var(--blue)">
        <div style="font-size:32px;margin-bottom:14px">🎭</div>
        <div style="font-size:16px;font-weight:500;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:8px">Vibe is invisible</div>
        <div class="body" style="font-size:14px">Is it loud or quiet? Local crowd or tourists? Worth the entry fee or not? No tool answers these in real time. You only find out when you're already there.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-gold a a6" style="margin-top:20px;padding:18px 24px">
      <div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text);line-height:1.6">💡 <strong>The hidden cost isn't bad nights out.</strong> It's the good nights that never happen — because 31 out of 35 people I interviewed said they regularly skip places entirely when they can't verify the vibe in advance.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 04: CORE INSIGHT -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="slide" id="s3">
  <div class="glow glow-g" style="width:800px;height:800px;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%)"></div>
  <div class="slide-tag">Core Insight</div>
  <div class="slide-inner" style="position:relative;z-index:1;align-items:center;text-align:center">
    <div class="eyebrow a a1" style="text-align:center">The insight that drives everything</div>
    <div class="display a a2" style="font-size:52px;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;line-height:1.3;max-width:820px;margin-bottom:28px">
      Every tool shows you the <span style="font-weight:700;font-style:normal;color:var(--gold)">best version</span> of a place.<br>Nobody shows you <span style="text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:var(--gold)">the real one.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="body a a3" style="font-size:18px;max-width:600px;margin:0 auto 36px">Vibe Check is the friend who's already been — telling you exactly what to expect before you get dressed and go.</div>
    <div class="flow a a4" style="justify-content:center">
      <div class="flow-step">Where are we going tonight?</div>
      <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step">Open Vibe Check</div>
      <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step">See what's actually happening</div>
      <div class="flow-arr">→</div>
      <div class="flow-step highlight">Decide in 30 seconds</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SLIDE 05: RESEARCH METHODOLOGY -->
